{
  "stem": "2723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose the first time, when things became very, very different-- first of all, we had to leave our home and go to a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the ghetto, my mother, who was just such a wonderful homemaker, tried, in that bleak, horrible building, to make a home for us, and did.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had two rooms that had everything in it-- kitchen, bathroom, the lot-- and an endlessly long corridor, which she sort of encouraged us to use as a sports ground, which was so incredible.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We ran up and down, and pretended we were having physical education, and all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In '42, my mother struggled to keep going and not to be [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] taken to Poland-- came to a very dangerous point, at which they rounded us up, because we were Jews, and we were three females.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother's sister, Susan, was a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She lived with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she, together with some other relatives, somehow marshaled enough help to try and get us out after a fortnight in a sort of a camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I suppose it was a holding situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Bratislava, in a disused factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think the rude shock came there, when my mother, whom I absolutely idealized and idolized, was continuously called to clean toilets.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had never seen my mother engaged in an activity of this sort.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very painful for me to see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I realized then that there was a total hopeless situation coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't aware what, but I could see the way they treated us that things could only get very ugly.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
